metadata.name: Arc 0 - Welcome to The Red Coven
metadata.description:
Nobody knows the origins of The Red Coven, it has existed since the dawn of time...  
Beautiful women with red skin holding great power has always been a myth for humans, a story that is told from generation to generation. 
A Great Mystery That we will discover together in this adventure.
